\ib  
\ip With the exception of the book of Revelation and John 7:53–8:11 the English Majority Text Version was translated from \add The Greek New Testament According to the Majority Text\add*, Second Edition, edited by Zane C. Hodges and Arthur L. Farstad, and published by Thomas Nelson in 1985. Revelation and John 7:53–8:11, were translate from \add The New Testament in the Original Greek: Byzantine Textform\add*, edited by Maurice A. Robinson and William G. Pierpont, and published by Chilton Book Publishing in 2005.  